Late David Audu Brand Journalists Association of Nigeria (BJAN) has announced March 3, 2023, for the interment of late David Audu, in his home town in Ofu Local Government Area in Kogi State. Untill his death, Audu was a member and erstwhile Secretary of BJAN, a body of writers that cover the Integrated marketing communications industry. He passed away on February 6, 2023, in his home town in Akpadidigbo , Ofu LGA of Kogi State after a brief illness.